_sText:
A tier 1, staged-linear map inspired by surf_ace.
Hey guys, this is my second map release and i'm excited to release this one.  It is a tier 1 map with 6 stages with one b-hop bonus.  This map is meant for newer surfers but has difficult skips for more skilled surfers.  There is also an easter egg for the memers who read this and can find it :)  Thanks to all the love and support from the community, hope you guys enjoy!
*Sorry for messing this upload up twice. last time I promise
